The paper discusses the performance of binary neural networks and proposes a new method to improve their accuracy. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the bias/variance trade-off and ensemble methods, which are also relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS).
